Package pw.ollie.politics.group

Class GroupProperty

  • java.lang.Object
    • pw.ollie.politics.group.GroupProperty
  • public final class GroupProperty
extends Object
    Contains static constant id numbers for various different Group properties, as well as helper methods relating to Group properties..
